reviewText: This has nothing to do with the seller or Amazon. Erotic Aquatics 2 is a total rip off. I saw the ORIGINAL Erotic Aquatics and this DVD is nothing more than snippits and bad edits form the original. With one guy/girl soft scene thrown in there. Its too bad but a lesson learned about OLD ADULT dvd's

Was original tape I thought I had ordered DVD. It was my mistake. Unfortunately though tape was in original condition, tape had warped was unable to load it. Tape came apart immediately and I had to throw it away.
